body:
Add Item-Fluid Combined Input/Output Hatch to [Modern Industrialization](https://modrinth.com/mod/modern-industrialization/) Mod.为[现代工业化](https://modrinth.com/mod/modern-industrialization/)模组添加同时支持物品和流体的总成仓。

Supports creating Item-Fluid Combined hatches using [KubeJS](https://modrinth.com/mod/kubejs):  
支持使用[KubeJS](https://modrinth.com/mod/kubejs)创建总成仓：

```js
// startup_scripts\*.js
MIMachineEvents.registerHatches(event => {
	 // Create a item-fluid combined hatch..
	// 创建一个总成仓。
	event.itemFluid("englishPrefix","prefix","casing",bucketCapacity, rows, columns); 
})
```
